x, y, z > 0
 x + y + z \leq 2 \left\{ \frac{x^2}{y+z} + \frac{y^2}{x+z} + \frac{z^2}{x+y} \right\} 
 x + y + z = \frac{x}{\sqrt{y+z}}\sqrt{y+z} + \frac{y}{\sqrt{x+z}}\sqrt{x+z} + \frac{z}{\sqrt{x+y}}\sqrt{x+y} 
 x + y + z = \frac{x}{\sqrt{y+z}}\sqrt{y+z} + \frac{y}{\sqrt{x+z}}\sqrt{x+z} + \frac{z}{\sqrt{x+y}}\sqrt{x+y}\le \left(\frac{x^2}{y+z}+\frac{y^2}{x+z}+\frac{z^2}{y+x}\right)^{1/2}(2x+2y+2z)^{1/2}.
